                  <rs id="t18580510-595-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18580510-595-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18580510-595-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Unlawfully uttering counterfeit coin, having other counterfeit coin in her possession.</rs>
